                                            span.main-title__summary FIELDS
                                            h2.main-title__text Steady your steps, we&nbsp;will go together!
                                        p Enjoying the vast expanse of&nbsp;the earth of grass, witnessing the splendor of&nbsp;River Svisloch country that
                                            | runs all over country, and spills to all&nbsp;corners&nbsp;This is&nbsp;so amazing at the beauty of the sun moving
                                            | of&nbsp;its bed or oversize enjoying&nbsp;the dim twilight from the Belarus canvas 
                                            | is an&nbsp;unforgettable expirience when visiting Belarus.
                                        a.arrow-link.arrow-link_centered(href="#")
                                            | read more
                                            .arrow-link__icon.icon__arrow_rightward
                section.section.section-cols
                    .section-col.section-col__content
                        .main-title.main-title_small
                            span.main-title__summary BELARUSIAN CULTURE
                            h2.main-title__text Our culture here is&nbsp;very friendly to&nbsp;people
                        p Known for his politeness, manners and gentleness. This becomes a&nbsp;characteristic when they mingle with others tribes and become basic traits that are passed down by&nbsp;their ancestors.
                        a.arrow-link(href="#")
                            | read more
                            .arrow-link__icon.icon__arrow_rightward
                    img.section-col.section-col__image(src="/images/culture.jpg" alt="Culture")
                section.section-border 
                    .start 
                        h2.start__title LIDus
                        .start__content 
